reviewText:
Just 3 statements why u should NOT buy this game:

1. predicatble and i'd say even trivial storyline;
2. gameplay mechanics are way to simple and repeatable (same run-n-hide stuff as in Outlast buy much easier);
3. game is too short (took me 2,8 hours to finish it) and definetely cant deliver all ideas that were meant to be delivered by developers.

The game looks more like a tech-demo for Oculus Rift crap.
To sum up this product is NOT worth its money.
